collection.name: YOU THE REAL MVP
collection.description:
A private group of 420 legendary MVPs of [Memeland](https://www.memeland.com). The NFT acts as the premium membership of the Memeland ecosystem. The perks include: 2 x Memeland main collection FREE mints, allowlist for all future 9GAG/Memeland NFT collections (e.g. POTATOZ), MVP role & MVP lounge in Discord, and more to come.

Read more on our Twitter: [@Memeland](https://www.twitter.com/memeland).
